Package: Bucephala
Type: Package
Title: Everything, Everywhere, All at Once
Version: 0.99.1
Authors@R: 
    person("David", "Rach", , "drach@som.umaryland.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2235-5585"))
Description:
  This R package is meant to simplify the setup of the scripts needed to parse the iLab schedule for
  various instruments, permiting visualizing on a separate monitor, as well tracking changes in the
  schedule with time. It is very much in early development, subject to my free time, and should not
  be used by any sane individual in its current form. 
